Class ComparisonOperators

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw5.db.ComparisonOperators

  • public class ComparisonOperators
extends java.lang.Object
    This class offers implementations of IComparisonOperator in form of static constants. They are also accessible via static method getComparisonOperator(String).
